    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>My best thanks for two favors. I am happy you got the books &amp; shall be
                    happier if they <del unit="words" quantity="1"/> meet approbation. never trouble
                        y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>self about the bird which I presume to be no
                    other than my Manks Petrel. Be so good as to send both the inclosed to <persName ref="pe0022">Doctor Ramsay</persName>. Should you meet <persName ref="pe0157">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Macgovan</persName> be so good as to
                    present my compliments &amp; let him know how glad I should be to have a drawing
                    of <rs ref="ar0065">his little image</rs>, which you may inclose to me I wish to
                    know where it was found.</p>
                <p>I think I heard an instance of a coach <gap reason="damage"/> pannels being broke
                    by y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Heralds <gap reason="damage" unit="letters" quantity="2"/>r assuming wrong arms. I wish you <gap reason="damage" unit="letters" quantity="1"/>ould furnish me with the year it was done. also
                    on what occasion &amp; to whose coach.</p>
                <p>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> third Letter with the agreable inclosure is this
                    moment arrived.</p>
                <closer><salute>I am, Dear Sir, y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> most obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Thomas Pennant</persName></signed>

                <dateline>June 7<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1774.</dateline></closer>

                <postscript>
                    <p>I hope to have y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> kind presents this week as I
                        hear they are at <placeName ref="pl0002">Chester</placeName>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine><unclear reason="illegible"> Too</unclear></addrLine>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom house</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburgh</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </p>
                <p><unclear reason="illegible"> Free <persName ref="pe0169">S
                        Salter</persName></unclear></p>
                <p><stamp><placeName ref="pl0703">NORTHOP</placeName></stamp></p>
                <p><stamp><placeName ref="pl0703">NORTHOP</placeName></stamp></p>
